name: Login Feature
description:
In Order to built own computer
  As a User
  I have to enter proper details

children.name: User should navigate to computer page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on computer menu
Then I should navigate to computer page successfully and verify the text "Computers"
User should navigate to desktop page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on computer menu
And I click on desktops link
Then I should navigate to desktops page successfully and verify the text "Desktops"
User should build own computer and add them to cart successfully

children.name: User should build own computer and add them to cart successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on computer menu
And I click on desktops link
And I click on build your own computer
And I select processor "2.2 GHz Intel Pentium Dual-Core E2200"
And I select RAM "2 GB"
And I select HDD "320 GB"
And I select OS "Vista Home [+$50.00]"
And I select software "Microsoft Office [+$50.00]"
And I click on add to cart button
Then I should get product added successfully message "The product has been added to your shopping cart"

name: Login Feature
description:
In Order to perform successful login
  As a User
  I have to enter correct username and password

children.name: User should navigate to login page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on login link
Then I should navigate to login page successfully and verify the message "Welcome, Please Sign In!"
Verify the error message with invalid credentials
Given I am on homepage
When I click on login link
And I enter email "abcd123@gmail.com"
And I enter password "abcd123"
And I click on login button
Then I should see the error message "Login was unsuccessful"
User should login successfully with valid credentials
Given I am on homepage
When I click on login link
And I enter email "abcdxyz123@gmail.com"
And I enter password "abcd@123"
And I click on login button
Then I should login successfully and verify the logout link

name: Register
description:
In Order to perform successful registration
  As a User
  I have to enter all the required field data

children.name: User should navigate to register page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on register link
Then I should navigate to register page successfully and verify the text "Register"
User should get mandatory field message
Given I am on homepage
When I click on register link
And I click on register button
Then I should get error message for first name required "First name is required."
And I should get error message for last name required "Last name is required."
And I should get error message for email required "Email is required."
And I should get error message for password required "Password is required."
And I should get error message for confirm password required "Password is required."
User should create account successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on register link
And I click on radio button against male
And I enter first name "om"
And I enter last name "patel"
And I select day for DOB "14"
And I select month for DOB "November"
And I select year for DOB "1999"
And I enter email for registration
And I enter password for registration "abcd123"
And I enter confirm password for registration "abcd123"
And I click on register for registration
Then I should get registration completion message "Your registration completed"
